channel.title: Errror when i run my server source
channel.description:
ok, so its been ok for about to days i dont think ive changed anything and suddenly i get this when i run my server(so its online)
Loading npcs... drops... spawn list...done! Exception in thread "Thread-2" java.lang.UnsupportedClassVersionError: client : Unsupported major.minor version 8242.8224 at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass1(Native Method) at java.lang.ClassLoader.defineClass(Unknown Source) at java.security.SecureClassLoader.defineClass(Unknow n Source) at java.net.URLClassLoader.defineClass(Unknown Source) at java.net.URLClassLoader.access$000(Unknown Source) at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(Unknown Source) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(Unknown Source) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClassInternal(Unknown Source) at itemspawning.LoadItems(itemspawning.java:18) at itemspawning.process(itemspawning.java:32) at process.run(process.java:29) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source)
so if anyone could help me and guide me on fixing this error id be very greatfull thanks,

item.dc:creator: @o.O_O.o o.O O.o
item.description:
@o.O_O.o wrote:

This is what I found, which makes sense:
“One or more of the classes you’re trying to load has been compiled with Java 5. Since you’re using JDK 1.4, it’s refusing to load the class because it (probably) uses Java 5 features that the VM doesn’t support.”
